                                             Company Snapshot
                                            









                                            
	Paz Oil Company Ltd operates in the Petroleum refining sector.
	
	In addition to historical fundamental analyses, the complete report available to purchase compares Paz Oil Company Ltd with three other
	petroleum refiners in Middle East:
		
	Israel Corporation Limited (The)
	
		(2016
	sales of 20.51 billion Israel Shekels [US$5.76  billion]
		of which 100%
		was Israel Chemicals),
	
	Oil Refineries Limited.
	
		(16.52 billion Israel Shekels [US$4.64  billion]
		of which 74%
		was Fuels), and
	
	Jordan Petroleum Refinery Company PSC
	
		which is
		
		based in Jordan
		(1.76 billion Jordanian Dinars [US$2.49  billion]
		of which 74%
		was Refineries & Distribution).
	
	Sales Analysis. 
	Paz Oil Company Ltd reported sales of 10.89 billion Israel Shekels (US$3.06 billion)
		for the
		
		year ending
		December of 2016.
	
		This
		
			represents
		
			a
			
			decrease of 15.4%
		
		 versus 2015, when the company's sales were 12.86 billion Israel Shekels.
	
		Contributing to the drop in overall sales was the 19.9% decline
		in Refining, from 4.95 billion Israel Shekels to 3.96 billion Israel Shekels.
		
					There were also decreases in sales in
					Retail and Trading (down 14.0% to 5.82 billion Israel Shekels)
				
					and
				Industry and Services (down 3.5% to 1.10 billion Israel Shekels)
				.
		

	




 


 
 


 
 


 
 











 



 













 










